OL,3,CThe forgotten forest: Brazil's
OL,4,Cvanishing Cerrado
OL,6,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew on how cattle ranching, crop
OL,8,Fcultivation, rising heat and worsening
OL,9,Fdrought are devastating Brazil's
OL,10,FCerrado forest
OL,12,FA Brazilian haven for wildlife, eight
OL,13,Ftimes the size of the UK, home to 30%
OL,14,Fof the country's biodiversity and 5%
OL,15,Fof the world's species.
OL,17,FNo, not the Amazon Rainforest - but
OL,18,Fthe Cerrado. This tropical savannah,
OL,19,Fabout a third the size of its more
OL,20,Ffamous neighbour, is disappearing far
OL,21,Fmore rapidly.
