OL,3,CThe forgotten forest: Brazil's
OL,4,Cvanishing Cerrado
OL,6,FThose roots also store vast amounts of
OL,7,Fcarbon. Satellite data tracking
OL,8,Fbiomass - the total amount of
OL,9,Fvegetation - reveals that
OL,10,Fdeforestation in the Cerrado has
OL,11,Freleased around 800 million tonnes of
OL,12,Fcarbon into the atmosphere since 2001.
OL,13,FThat's equivalent to two years' worth
OL,14,Fof the UK's total emissions.
OL,16,FRoughly a thousand miles upstream from
OL,17,Fwhere we filmed on the mighty
OL,18,FTocantins River lies the city of
OL,19,FBelem, in the Amazon region.
