OL,3,CThe forgotten forest: Brazil's
OL,4,Cvanishing Cerrado
OL,6,FOn Thursday, world leaders will gather
OL,7,Fthere for the opening of COP30. One of
OL,8,Fthis year's major climate conference
OL,9,Fgoals will be reducing deforestation.
OL,11,FBrazil's President Lula, who achieved
OL,12,Fsuccess in curbing deforestation
OL,13,Fduring a previous term, is pledging $1
OL,14,Fbillion to the Tropical Forests
OL,15,FForever Fund. Yet questions remain
OL,16,Fover whether his rhetoric will match
OL,17,Freality.
