OL,3,CThe forgotten forest: Brazil's
OL,4,Cvanishing Cerrado
OL,6,FTens of thousands of acres of
OL,7,Frainforest have already been cleared
OL,8,Fto make way for a new four-lane
OL,9,Fhighway - partly to deliver delegates
OL,10,Fto the conference in Belem.
OL,12,FThe government has also recently
OL,13,Fapproved oil exploration licences near
OL,14,Fthe mouth of the Amazon and is
OL,15,Fconsidering lifting a ban on soy grown
OL,16,Fin deforested areas of the rainforest.
